data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER!!
This home is VERY maintained!! It’s clean and like new home complete with Party Patio including light string, stained concrete, built in cabinets, bar and speakers. Multiple UPGRADES such as the patio, game room, water softener, a whole-house water FILTRATION system, security system, cameras, surround system and more. Great layout with an open concept living to kitchen which allows the chef in your family to be a part of the party while preparing for friends and family. Walking distance to the schools, local shopping, and food! This neighborhood has a POOL and PARK! The community park that’s CONNECTED to this family-friendly neighborhood has a fishing pond and a splash pad for kids with tennis courts, sand volleyball, basketball, and so much more! Buyer to verify all information.
BACK ON MARKET DUE TO RELOCATION!
*Pre Approval or proof of funds ONLY and must be sent to agent before the showing*
